    "AD": "Donate it! Here are some ideas for what do to:<ul><li>You can place it in a box outside your home so people who pass by can pick it up. But be sure to not put anything in there that would be dangerous for kids or animals. And be sure to take care of it, when there are items left and not let it rot on the street.</li><li>You could bring it to a charity shop.</li><li>Maybe you know someone who would really love this and you can gift it to them (but be sure that they *really* would love to have it, nobody wants to feel like you're unloading their junk onto them)</li></ul>",
    "AE": "Here are some ideas for how to find out:<ul><li>Ask someone you know</li><li>Look into a marketplace for used goods and see if people are putting stuff like this online</li><li>Bring to a charity shop and ask them if they would accept it. They have a feeling for what they will be able to resell and what not</li></ul>Ask around until you have an answer as to whether other people would stil use it.",
